tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE nutritional_composition_of_feed (
    feed_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    feed_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    protein_content FLOAT NOT NULL,
    carbohydrate_content FLOAT NOT NULL,
    fat_content FLOAT NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE feed_composition (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    protein FLOAT NOT NULL,
    carbohydrates FLOAT NOT NULL,
    fats FLOAT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE livestock (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    species VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    age INT NOT NULL,
    weight FLOAT NOT NULL,
    feed_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (feed_id) REFERENCES feed_composition(id)
);

CREATE TABLE feed_composition (
  feed_id INT,
  protein_percentage FLOAT,
  carbohydrate_percentage FLOAT,
  fat_percentage FLOAT,
  PRIMARY KEY (feed_id)
);

CREATE TABLE livestock (
  livestock_id INT,
  name VARCHAR(50),
  species VARCHAR(50),
  weight FLOAT,
  age INT,
  PRIMARY KEY (livestock_id)
);

CREATE TABLE feeding_schedule (
  feed_id INT,
  livestock_id INT,
  feeding_time TIMESTAMP,
  quantity FLOAT,
  FOREIGN KEY (feed_id) REFERENCES feed_composition (feed_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (livestock_id) REFERENCES livestock (livestock_id)
);

CREATE TABLE livestock (
    livestock_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    species VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    weight FLOAT,
    feed_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (feed_id) REFERENCES feed_composition(feed_id)
);

CREATE TABLE animal_feeds (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    feed_name VARCHAR(100),
    protein FLOAT,
    carbohydrates FLOAT,
    fat FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE animals (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    animal_type VARCHAR(50),
    animal_name VARCHAR(100),
    age INT,
    weight FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE feed_categories (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50),
    description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE feed_usage (
    feed_id INT,
    animal_id INT,
    feed_quantity FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (feed_id) REFERENCES animal_feeds(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (animal_id) REFERENCES animals(id)
)

CREATE TABLE feed_analysis (
    feed_id INT,
    protein_content FLOAT,
    carbohydrates_content FLOAT,
    fat_content FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (feed_id) REFERENCES animal_feeds(id)
)
